name: Slice Me Tender
description:
I don't exactly like tomatoes. They are somewhat squishy and when slicing them, the jello squishy insides will slide out, making it impossible to slice or cut it perfectly. It's absolutely annoying, trying to add some tomatoes to my meal.

Just like annoying Mondays.
A whole day to squish your insides out while you feel like being sliced to pieces.
